snippet.title: 8000 Subscriber Special - With Guests
snippet.description:
Well, isn't it about time I did one of these? I think so! So to celebrate 8000+ channel members I am going to have a Channel review + Q&A + Guests in what should hopefully be a 3 hour live stream later today.

Help me get more NASA logo clobber Paypal? https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/RantyFE

Support the channel on Patreon? https://www.patreon.com/flerfspective
If anyone wants to adopt a Flerf, or any of the other levels https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw1YnIqAcKpHZYAQytaEVOg/join
